Injury burden in individuals aged 50 years or older in the Eastern Mediterranean 
region, 1990-2019: a systematic analysis from the Global Burden of Disease Study 
2019.

Al-Hajj S(1), Farran S(2), Sibai AM(1), Hamadeh RR(3), Rahimi-Movaghar V(4), 
Al-Raddadi RM(5), Sadeghian F(6), Ghodsi Z(4), Alhajyaseeh W(7), Rmeileh NMA(8), 
Mokdad AH(9); GBD 2019 Collaborators.

Author information:
(1)Faculty of Health Sciences, American University of Beirut, Beirut, Lebanon.
(2)Faculty of Medicine, American University of Beirut, Beirut, Lebanon.
(3)College of Medicine and Medical Sciences, Arabian Gulf University, Manama, 
