Xeroderma pigmentosum: an updated review.

Leung AK(1)(2), Barankin B(3), Lam JM(4)(5), Leong KF(6), Hon KL(7)(8).

Author information:
(1)Department of Pediatrics, The University of Calgary, Calgary, Alberta, 
Canada.
(2)The Alberta Children's Hospital, Calgary, Alberta, Canada.
(3)Toronto Dermatology Centre, Toronto, Ontario, Canada.
(4)Department of Pediatrics and Department of Dermatology and Skin Sciences, 
University of British Columbia, Vancouver, British Columbia, Canada.
(5)BC Children's Hospital, Vancouver, British Columbia, Canada.
(6)Pediatric Institute, Kuala Lumpur General Hospital, Kuala Lumpur, Malaysia.
(7)Department of Paediatrics, Hong Kong Institute of Integrative Medicine, The 
Chinese University of Hong Kong, Hong Kong.
(8)Jockey Club School of Public Health and Primary Care, The Chinese University 
